# LLM Studio Roadmap

## Phase 1: Foundation (Q3 2024)
- Completion of core platform development.
- Integration with primary blockchain networks.
- Beta testing with select Web3 projects.
- Launch of unified dashboard and workflow automation features.

## Phase 2: Expansion (Q4 2024)
- Addition of advanced analytics and reporting modules.
- Enhanced security features, including multi-factor authentication.
- Support for additional blockchain protocols.
- User onboarding improvements and comprehensive documentation release.

## Phase 3: Community & Ecosystem Building (Q1 2025)
- Launch of community forums and support channels.
- Introduction of plugin or API support for third-party integrations.
- Partnerships with other Web3 tool providers.

## Phase 4: Long-term Vision (Mid-2025 and beyond)
- Continuous platform enhancement driven by user feedback.
- Expansion into broader decentralized application lifecycle management.
- Exploration of AI-driven project management tools.

This roadmap is designed to deliver tangible value incrementally while adapting to the rapidly evolving Web3 ecosystem.